## Bind outlet to third shop ID

The "third shop ID" refers to the outlet's ID in your own system. In this step, you need to bind your outlet ID with the outlet ID created by TikTok GO.

1.  Log into your Merchant Portal account.
2.  Under the **Manage Outlets** tab, click the **Outlet data** dropdown, then click **Upload application ID**.

![](https://sf16-sg.tiktokcdn.com/obj/tiktok-open-platform-sg/ttop_doc_images/b9a2684982e299129991c2eb88e83cf4)

1.  Click on the **Download** button to download the spreadsheet file.

![](https://sf16-sg.tiktokcdn.com/obj/tiktok-open-platform-sg/ttop_doc_images/c1e43afa7413fbb5a49c13c730dc73ff)

1.  Add the following information to the file:

1.  Client Access Key of this merchant, you may copy it from the main page
2.  TikTok Outlet ID which you can copy from the **Manage outlets** page
3.  Third\_shop\_ID which should be your outlet ID in your own system

3.  Save the file then upload it.
4.  Click **Confirm** button to submit the file.



